# Upstash Redis Configuration (Rate Limiting)
# Get these from: https://console.upstash.com/

# Redis REST URL
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://your-database.upstash.io

# Redis REST Token
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=your-token-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://console.upstash.com/
# 2. Sign in or create free account (no credit card required!)
# 3. Click "Create Database"
# 4. Choose:
#    - Type: Regional (fastest)
#    - Region: US East (or closest to your users)
#    - Name: heyberkshire-rate-limit
#    - Enable: TLS (recommended)
# 5. Click "Create"
# 6. Copy "REST URL" → UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL
# 7. Copy "REST Token" → UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN
# 8. Add both to .env.local for development
# 9. Add both to Vercel environment variables for production
#
# Free Tier Limits:
# - 10,000 commands per day
# - 256MB storage
# - Perfect for rate limiting!
